        </div>
        <a class="tv2-more" href={`${base}/talent/people/`}>
          <span data-tc>全部 {stats.peopleCount} →</span>
          <span data-sc>全部 {stats.peopleCount} →</span>
        </a>
      </header>
      <p class="tv2-section-lede">
        <span data-tc>優先列出 <strong>⚡-評級</strong> 且機構已關聯或有社交提及的研究員。</span>
        <span data-sc>优先列出 <strong>⚡-评级</strong> 且机构已关联或有社交提及的研究员。</span>
      </p>
      <div class="picks-grid">
        {watchlist.map(p => <PersonCard record={p} />)}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══ Methodology — collapsed by default ══════════════════════════════ -->
    <details class="tv2-method">
      <summary>
        <span class="tv2-method-summary-label">
          <span data-tc>方法論 · How this works</span>
          <span data-sc>方法论 · How this works</span>
        </span>
        <span class="tv2-method-summary-cue" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
      </summary>
      <ol class="tv2-method-list">
        <li><strong>Subdirections</strong> — 方法族趨勢來自 <code>field-state-*.json</code> + <code>ai-field-state-*.json</code>（機械化，零 LLM）。加速度 = (近 7d − 前 7d) / max(前值, 1)。</li>
        <li><strong>Labs</strong> — 來自 <code>entity-index.json</code> 的 <code>type=lab</code> 實體，90 日滾動窗口。</li>
        <li><strong>People</strong> — <code>vla-daily-rating-out-*.json</code> 第一作者抽取 + <code>entity-index.json</code> <code>type=researcher</code> 合併，機構經 <code>institution-registry.json</code> 解析。</li>
        <li><strong>HR Queue</strong> — People 上加門檻：頂評 ≥ 🔧、90 日 ≥ 2 篇、機構可解析、聯繫狀態非 <em>not_linked</em>。</li>
        <li><strong>Email 永不儲存或顯示</strong> — 僅 <code>contact_status</code> 枚舉：<em>linked_via_lab</em> / <em>social_mention</em> / <em>not_linked</em>。任何觸達前請自行核實。</li>
      </ol>
    </details>

